I'm scared just saying "hi" to a girl.

389
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,100
你做得不错
You're doing fine.

390
00:24:33,470 --> 00:24:35,330
嘿 你能...
Hey, can you ever, like...

391
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:38,130
离开这儿吗?
get outta here?

392
00:24:38,130 --> 00:24:40,820
比如一天 或者...
On a day pass or...

393
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:44,120
是的 我是自愿来这儿的
Yeah. I'm here voluntarily.

394
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:45,840
好吧...
Well...

395
00:24:46,930 --> 00:24:49,200
你想做点...
Would you like to...

396
00:24:49,230 --> 00:24:50,900
什么吗?
do something?

397
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:53,210
