You mean...

398
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:56,150
约会?
a date?

399
00:24:56,290 --> 00:24:57,630
嗯...
Uh...

400
00:24:58,430 --> 00:25:00,130
是的
Yeah.

401
00:25:03,230 --> 00:25:05,610
我愿意
I'd love that.

402
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:12,170
想一下 Desmond...
Remind me, Desmond...

403
00:25:12,170 --> 00:25:14,850
