And here you are, back for more.

406
00:25:19,930 --> 00:25:22,680
要是我不清楚内情的话 我肯定会说这座岛与你有关
If I didn't know better, I'd say this island has it in for you.

407
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:24,230
你清楚内情吗?
Do you know better?

408
00:25:24,230 --> 00:25:25,410
什么?
Excuse me?

409
00:25:25,410 --> 00:25:27,790
