是的 他也可能会那么做
Yeah, he could.

471
00:29:28,190 --> 00:29:30,280
我在那里没有看到Jacob
I didn't see Jacob back there.

472
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:34,130
呃 我那么说 仅仅是想让大家听从我
Uh, I just said it because I wanted everyone to listen to me.

473
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:37,580
我知道的
I know.

